title: Altamont and The Bionic Ear Present: Girl Tears
description:
SoCal hardcore band, Girl Tears, hit up the Bionic Ear recently and recorded two songs for their limited edition 7 inch.

Here's an edit from that session recorded at The Bionic Ear.
